    <title>今日有雨，微凉</title>
    <updated>2005-06-29T00:00:00+08:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Bozhidar Batsov</name>
      <uri>http://www.batsov.com/</uri>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;倦意颇浓，无他。&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;世界的确未因我的不关注而停转，很好。&lt;a&gt;&lt;img /&gt;screen.width/2)this.width=screen.width/2;&amp;#039; &amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;
</content>
